<para id="fs-id4256908">C</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-id1604554">
<problem id="fs-id1225759"><para id="fs-id1758232">Which of these cranial nerves contains preganglionic parasympathetic fibers?</para>
<list id="fs-id1481474" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>optic, CN II</item>
<item>facial, CN VII</item>
<item>trigeminal, CN V</item>
<item>hypoglossal, CN XII</item>
