<exercise id="fs-id2766993">
<problem id="fs-id2522634"><para id="fs-id2522635">Which of the following is<emphasis effect="italics"> not</emphasis> a target of a sympathetic preganglionic fiber?</para>
<list id="fs-id1610997" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>intermural ganglion</item>
<item>collateral ganglion</item>
<item>adrenal gland</item>
<item>chain ganglion</item>
